{
  "id": "69e679092769ea45c335dc86",
  "title": "本日の教訓 2026-04-21 suto3",
  "created": 1776711954,
  "updated": 1776762993,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69e679092769ea45c335dc86",
      "text": "本日の教訓 2026-04-21 suto3",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776711954,
      "updated": 1776711954
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6872b0000000000b69401",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/d43137deebe484f6a41ad4fc47ff2eec]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776715563,
      "updated": 1776715564
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6872d0000000000b69402",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776715565,
      "updated": 1776715565
    },
    {
      "id": "69e679110000000000b693e5",
      "text": "[suto3.icon]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776711954,
      "updated": 1776711966
    },
    {
      "id": "69e679200000000000b693e8",
      "text": "あなたが「やめて」と言ったのなら、私はやめます",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776711969,
      "updated": 1776712036
    },
    {
      "id": "69e679640000000000b693eb",
      "text": "だから、私が「やめて」と言ったら、あなたもやめてください",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776712037,
      "updated": 1776712233
    },
    {
      "id": "69e679200000000000b693e9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776711969,
      "updated": 1776711969
    },
    {
      "id": "69e679c10000000000b693ec",
      "text": "　これは、[共通認識]にできるだろうか",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776712130,
      "updated": 1776712736
    },
    {
      "id": "69e67ccc0000000000b693f9",
      "text": "　　（私は、共通認識だと思っていたのだが、どうやら違うようだ）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776712908,
      "updated": 1776712970
    },
    {
      "id": "69e67a170000000000b693ed",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776712216,
      "updated": 1776712216
    },
    {
      "id": "69e67a170000000000b693ee",
      "text": "私が「やめて」と言っても、あなたがやめないのなら",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776712216,
      "updated": 1776712343
    },
    {
      "id": "69e67a720000000000b693ef",
      "text": "あなたが「やめて」と言っても、わたしはやめません",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776712307,
      "updated": 1776712393
    },
    {
      "id": "69e679200000000000b693ea",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776711969,
      "updated": 1776711969
    },
    {
      "id": "69e67aca0000000000b693f0",
      "text": "　たぶん、これはあかんやつ（うまく言えないけど）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776712395,
      "updated": 1776712739
    },
    {
      "id": "69e67aca0000000000b693f1",
      "text": "　ポリシーとしては一貫しているけど",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776712395,
      "updated": 1776718157
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6bdc50000000000e1743b",
      "text": "　[憎しみの連鎖]を産むやつ（青リンクだ）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776729541,
      "updated": 1776729586
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6912a0000000000b69408",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776718123,
      "updated": 1776718123
    },
    {
      "id": "69e691580000000000b69409",
      "text": "[ダブルスタンダード]は良くない",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776718169,
      "updated": 1776718219
    },
    {
      "id": "69e691580000000000b6940a",
      "text": "　これも、[共通認識]にできているだろうか",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776718169,
      "updated": 1776718312
    },
    {
      "id": "69e692080000000000b6940e",
      "text": "　建前としてはともかく、現実問題としてはダブルスタンダードは多い",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776718345,
      "updated": 1776718468
    },
    {
      "id": "69e692380000000000b6940f",
      "text": "　　（わたしはいいけど、あなたはだめ、というやつ）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776718393,
      "updated": 1776718832
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6918c0000000000b6940b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776718220,
      "updated": 1776718220
    },
    {
      "id": "69e67aca0000000000b693f2",
      "text": "　日記をふたつに分けたほうがいいかな",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776712395,
      "updated": 1776712685
    },
    {
      "id": "69e67bbb0000000000b693f4",
      "text": "　　まじめな日記",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776712636,
      "updated": 1776712705
    },
    {
      "id": "69e67c030000000000b693f7",
      "text": "　　ふざけた日記",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776712707,
      "updated": 1776712719
    },
    {
      "id": "69e67bf10000000000b693f5",
      "text": "  日記を分けても、どちらも同じ感じになる可能性もあるのか",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776712690,
      "updated": 1776719309
    },
    {
      "id": "69e695ce0000000000b69412",
      "text": "  　悪意、じゃなくて（自主規制）が割り込んでくる可能性は排除できない",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776719311,
      "updated": 1776719382
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6957c0000000000b69411",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776719229,
      "updated": 1776719229
    },
    {
      "id": "69e699900000000000fd7809",
      "text": "　いっそのこと日記ページを1日に 100ページつくるとか",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776720272,
      "updated": 1776720351
    },
    {
      "id": "69e699df0000000000fd780b",
      "text": "　　本物はひとつだけ、残りはダミー",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776720352,
      "updated": 1776720385
    },
    {
      "id": "69e69cbc0000000000b69415",
      "text": "　　　いろいろあかんやつ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776721085,
      "updated": 1776721094
    },
    {
      "id": "69e699a40000000000fd780a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776720293,
      "updated": 1776720293
    },
    {
      "id": "69e67c5d0000000000b693f8",
      "text": "　あと、[ふーこ]さんになりきって日記を書くという手段も考えられるが、さすがにこれはキモいだろう",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776712797,
      "updated": 1776721152
    },
    {
      "id": "69e698f60000000000b69414",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776720119,
      "updated": 1776720119
    },
    {
      "id": "69e689a30000000000fd7801",
      "text": "　[KEEP OUT.icon] は使わないほうがいいな",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776716196,
      "updated": 1776716231
    },
    {
      "id": "69e689cd0000000000fd7803",
      "text": "　　規制の対象にしたい人にはほとんど効果がない",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776716238,
      "updated": 1776716313
    },
    {
      "id": "69e68a000000000000fd7804",
      "text": "　　規制の対象にしたくない人には過剰に効いてしまう",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776716289,
      "updated": 1776716368
    },
    {
      "id": "69e68a510000000000fd7805",
      "text": "　　逆効果だね",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776716369,
      "updated": 1776716387
    },
    {
      "id": "69e689a30000000000fd7802",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776716196,
      "updated": 1776716196
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6d1450000000000e17444",
      "text": " 井戸端で書きたい欲",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776734533,
      "updated": 1776734592
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6d1510000000000e17446",
      "text": " 　が定期的に湧いてくるんだよな",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776734545,
      "updated": 1776734573
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6da7a0000000000fd7815",
      "text": " 　井戸端で書くときに注意すること（自分用）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776736891,
      "updated": 1776762662
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6db350000000000fd781a",
      "text": " 　　暗黙の前提や暗黙の了解事項はないものとして考える",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776737078,
      "updated": 1776762672
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6db6b0000000000fd781b",
      "text": " 　　　[低コンテキスト文化]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776737131,
      "updated": 1776737150
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6dbb40000000000fd781c",
      "text": " 　　　書かないとわからないし、書いても読んでくれるとは限らない",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776737204,
      "updated": 1776762681
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6dc0b0000000000fd781d",
      "text": " 　　　逆に暗黙の前提や暗黙の了解事項を押し付けられることもある",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776737291,
      "updated": 1776762685
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6dd910000000000fd7824",
      "text": " 　　　　[高コンテキスト文化]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776737682,
      "updated": 1776737699
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6ddaa0000000000fd7825",
      "text": " 　　　　理解するのに高いコストを強いられる",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776737707,
      "updated": 1776762691
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6dabd0000000000fd7817",
      "text": " 　　複数行に分けない",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776736957,
      "updated": 1776762697
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6dadf0000000000fd7818",
      "text": " 　　　切り取られるから",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776736991,
      "updated": 1776762707
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6dfce0000000000fd7827",
      "text": "  　　　書いたことの意味が変わってしまうから",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776738255,
      "updated": 1776762720
    },
    {
      "id": "69e725840000000000ba74fe",
      "text": "  　編集しやすいように書かない",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776756101,
      "updated": 1776762724
    },
    {
      "id": "69e725b20000000000ba74ff",
      "text": " 　　　切り取られるから",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776756147,
      "updated": 1776762731
    },
    {
      "id": "69e73f6b000000000073b512",
      "text": " 　　　変な編集をされないように書く",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776762732,
      "updated": 1776762767
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6dc4b0000000000fd781e",
      "text": " 　　凝った表現は使わない",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776737356,
      "updated": 1776762801
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6dc6e0000000000fd7820",
      "text": " 　　　読む人によっては理解できないから",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776737390,
      "updated": 1776762807
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6e60a00000000007efe20",
      "text": " 　　　理解力のない人に誤解されるから",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776739851,
      "updated": 1776762814
    },
    {
      "id": "69e726520000000000ba7501",
      "text": " 　　単純な文にする",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776756307,
      "updated": 1776762820
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6e23d00000000007efe1d",
      "text": " 　　強い表現は使わない",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776738877,
      "updated": 1776762833
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6e24c00000000007efe1f",
      "text": " 　　　誤解されるから",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776738893,
      "updated": 1776762837
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6e3330000000000fd7828",
      "text": " 　　　だいたい悪い方の意味にとられるから",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776739124,
      "updated": 1776762841
    },
    {
      "id": "69e73fd9000000000073b513",
      "text": " 　　　[クッション言葉]を入れる",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776762842,
      "updated": 1776762870
    },
    {
      "id": "69e7268b0000000000ba7502",
      "text": " 　　当たり障りのない表現にする",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776756363,
      "updated": 1776762884
    },
    {
      "id": "69e74005000000000073b515",
      "text": " 　　 尖った表現は誤解を招きやすい",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776762885,
      "updated": 1776762919
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6e36a0000000000fd782a",
      "text": " 　　冗談は通じない",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776739178,
      "updated": 1776762928
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6e4710000000000fd782c",
      "text": " 　　　特にブラックジョークは禁止",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776739441,
      "updated": 1776762950
    },
    {
      "id": "69e726bd0000000000ba7504",
      "text": " 　　皮肉は通じない",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776756413,
      "updated": 1776762937
    },
    {
      "id": "69e726be0000000000ba7505",
      "text": " 　　　皮肉を理解するには高い教養が必要",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776756415,
      "updated": 1776762943
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6e4de0000000000fd782d",
      "text": " 　　自分の意見を言うときは特に気をつける",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776739551,
      "updated": 1776762958
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6e4f90000000000fd782e",
      "text": " 　　 命令と受け取る人がいる",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776739577,
      "updated": 1776762963
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6da960000000000fd7816",
      "text": " 　　「光る言葉」は隠す",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776736918,
      "updated": 1776762967
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6dc950000000000fd7821",
      "text": " 　　　必要以上に注目をあびることになる",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776737429,
      "updated": 1776762977
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6dcc50000000000fd7822",
      "text": " 　　　他の大事なところは読んでもらえない",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776737478,
      "updated": 1776762982
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6db0e0000000000fd7819",
      "text": " 　　あとは何があるだろう",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776737039,
      "updated": 1776762987
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6d1450000000000e17445",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776734533,
      "updated": 1776762993
    },
    {
      "id": "69e679110000000000b693e6",
      "text": "#2026-04-21",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776711954,
      "updated": 1776711969
    }
  ]
}